  20  6  2  1  first spectroscopic symbol (SS) in each of 4 "QSs.inp"; here SS=25 for O-like Ge
  32  6  2  1  SS of H-like ion in each of 4 "QSs.inp". NIF code doesn't accept SS[H] > 36
815  2  2  2  nucleus # in 4 "QSs.inp". 
2098  2  2  2  number of states in each of 4 "QSs.inp"; NIF code doesn't accept > 2300 states. 
